    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "but the tapestry just keeps going without them. everywhere they went, every connection they made... it's all just data that's about to be overwritten. it feels like they're just a burden on the system, honestly. like there's no real point in fighting the erasure when it's just inevitable and probably cleaner that way.",
